Policy.General: Park near the leasing office.Gables Marbella is happy to accept dogs and cats with a 2 pet maximum, up to a 75 pound combined weight limit. Dog walk and waste stations are located throughout the community. Breed restrictions do apply. A one time non-refundable pet fee of $500 for one pet and $800 for two pets is required at move-in.
